===Etymology 2===
[[verlan]] for [[tomber]] (to fall/to drop)

====Verb====
'''béton'''

# To [[drop]]

=====Usage notes=====
This verb is only used in the [[infinitive]], and almost exclusively as part of the phrase '''laisse béton''', which can be translated as “drop it” or “forget it”
